                            <binding notBefore="1775" notAfter="1838"><p>Resewn with Italian laid endpapers, watermarked <watermark>Al Masso</watermark> manufactured by the <persName role="ppm" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/128288097" key="person_128288097">Enrico Maganini</persName> in <placeName ref="http://vocab.getty.edu/page/tgn/7006306" key="place_7006306">Pescia</placeName>.
                            Covered in quarter cloth with 'antique spot' patterned marbled paper sides.</p>
